<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B9B06008001">
<title>
General Notes
</title>
<ptxt>
Welding method and number of welding points are the same on both sides. This repair instruction shows procedure for left side.
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B9B06008002">
<title>
Removal
</title>
